original: Öman, Bror, tandläkare, Borås, f. 24/3/00 i Öra, Älvsb. 1., av August Ö. o. Klara Larsson. G. 20/1/29 m. Magda Karlsson. Barn: Margareta f. 19/ 12/29, Birgitta o. Siv 32. — Stud:ex. i Skara 18, med. kand. i Upps. 25, tand-läk. 28. Praktik i Borås sed. 28.
translated: Öman, Bror, dentist, Borås, b. 24/3/00 in Öra, Älvsb. 1., son of August Ö. and Klara Larsson. Married on 20/1/29 to Magda Karlsson. Children: Margareta b. 19/12/29, Birgitta and Siv b. 32. Completed secondary school in Skara in 1918, obtained a medical degree in Uppsala in 1925, and became a dentist in 1928. Practiced in Borås since 1928.
